eZpeda extension FEATURES
=================================

eZpedia provides for an eZ Publish based wiki solution

1) eZpedia extension features available and related sources

The eZpedia extension provides the following features

   - eZpedia eZ Publish extension site design templates
   -- See related sources: design/

   - eZpedia eZ Publish extension export shell scripts
   -- See related sources: bin/

   - eZpedia eZ Publish extension docroot files
   -- See related sources: files/

   - eZpedia eZ Publish extension module views
   -- See related sources: module/

   - eZpedia eZ Publish extension kernel override classes
   -- See related sources: kernel/

   - eZpedia eZ Publish extension share locale for eng-GB
   -- See related sources: share/

   - eZpedia eZ Publish extension settings
   -- See related sources: settings/

